<plot>A bandit terrorizes a small Mexican farming village each year. Several of the village elders send three of the farmers into the United States to search for gunmen to defend them. They end up with 7, each of whom comes for a different reason. They must prepare the town to repulse an army of over 100 bandits who will arrive wanting food. An Americanization of the film, _Shichinin no samurai (1954)_ (qv)</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?573618</url></doc>
